refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
abstract public Ds\SequenceDs\Sequence::sorted callablecomparator
Retorna uma cópia ordenada, usando uma função de comparação comparator opcional.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Exemplo de Ds\Sequence::sorted


<?php
$sequence = new \Ds\Vector([4, 5, 1, 3, 2]);

print_r($sequence->sorted());
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


Ds\Vector Object
(
    [0] => 1
    [1] => 2
    [2] => 3
    [3] => 4
    [4] => 5
)




   Exemplo de Ds\Sequence::sorted usando um comparador


<?php
$sequence = new \Ds\Vector([4, 5, 1, 3, 2]);

$sorted = $sequence->sorted(function($a, $b) {
    return $b <=> $a;
});

print_r($sorted);
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


Ds\Vector Object
(
    [0] => 5
    [1] => 4
    [2] => 3
    [3] => 2
    [4] => 1
)
